data.description: The beautiful and popular Lancaster A plan built by Grant. 2 bedrooms downstairs and 3 bedrooms upstairs plus huge bonus room!  Large primary bedroom with walk through bathroom and  laundry room with built in shelves. Primary bathroom with free standing tub. The kitchen of your dreams awaits with large center island, breakfast area, quartz countertops, 5 burner gas cooktop with range hood, and farm sink! 3 car garage, water view and extended back porch on a half acre lot. Call today for your personal showing.
